snippet.title: Unkindess - Asylum Jam 2015 Trailer
snippet.description:
Download The Free Demo for Unkindness now!
itch.io page: http://andrearitsu.itch.io/unkindness

Asylum Jam - Unkindness' Page: http://www.asylumjam.com/games/unkindness-asylum-jam-demo/107282

Asylum Jam is an annual game jam about creating horror games devoted to not play up negative mental health tropes. This is the second year I took part in it.

Please read more here: www.asylumjam.com/

Support me on Patreon if you want to
https://www.patreon.com/andrearitsu

Follow Andrea's Adventures on the Internet
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/andrearitsu
Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/andrearitsu/
